Hi, my name is Jace Jahraus. I have a passion for continued learning which has helped me become a successful programmer along with a strong ability to problem solving. I have a Diploma in Web and Mobile Applications Development and have two years of experience in the workforce as a Web and Applications Developer.


I am seeking a full-time position, either remote in Australia or local to the Brisbane or Sunshine Coast area.
